stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> created : User initiates action

    created --> submitted : Frontend sends tx to chain
    created --> failed : Preparation error

    submitted --> pending : Tx broadcast to network
    submitted --> failed : Signing rejected

    pending --> confirmed : Block confirmation received
    pending --> failed : Tx reverted on-chain

    confirmed --> [*]
    failed --> [*]

    state created {
        [*] --> intent_collected
        intent_collected --> quote_fetched
        quote_fetched --> tx_prepared
        tx_prepared --> awaiting_signature
    }

    state confirmed {
        [*] --> receipt_parsed
        receipt_parsed --> amounts_extracted
        amounts_extracted --> gateway_updated
    }

    note right of created
        Gateway transaction API creates record:
        - action (swap/supply/stake)
        - fromAsset, toAsset
        - fromAmount
        - walletId, chainId
    end note

    note right of confirmed
        Receipt processing:
        - Extract gas fees
        - Extract actual output amount
        - Calculate exchange rate
        - Update gateway record
    end note
